276 | ### 6. Initial Pose Consistency
277 | 
278 | **Check:** Initial joint positions in SDF match canonical standing pose.
279 | 
280 | **Canonical Standing Pose (from AGENTS.md):**
281 | ```python
282 | HIP_STAND  = -0.09  # rad
283 | KNEE_STAND =  0.35  # rad
284 | ANKLE_STAND = 0.0   # rad (fixed joint)
285 | ```
286 | 
287 | **Validation Logic:**
288 | ```python
289 | STANDING_POSE = {
290 |     'l_hip_pitch': -0.09,
291 |     'r_hip_pitch': -0.09,
292 |     'l_knee': 0.35,
293 |     'r_knee': 0.35,
294 |     'l_ankle': 0.0,
295 |     'r_ankle': 0.0,
296 | }
297 | 
298 | # Check initial_position in JointPositionController
299 | for match in re.finditer(r'<plugin filename="gz-sim-joint-position-controller-system".*?>(.*?)</plugin>', 
300 |                           sdf_content, re.DOTALL):
301 |     block = match.group(1)
302 |     joint = re.search(r'<joint_name>([^<]+)</joint_name>', block).group(1)
303 |     
304 |     init_pos_match = re.search(r'<initial_position>([^<]+)</initial_position>', block)
305 |     if init_pos_match:
306 |         init_pos = float(init_pos_match.group(1))
307 |         
308 |         if joint in STANDING_POSE:
309 |             expected = STANDING_POSE[joint]
310 |             if abs(init_pos - expected) > 0.01:
311 |                 print(f"⚠️  Joint '{joint}': initial_position {init_pos:.3f} "
312 |                       f"doesn't match standing pose {expected:.3f}")
313 | 
314 | # Check initial_position in joint definition
315 | for match in re.finditer(r'<joint name="([^"]+)".*?<initial_position>([^<]+)</initial_position>', 
316 |                           sdf_content, re.DOTALL):
317 |     joint, init_pos = match.groups()
318 |     init_pos = float(init_pos)
319 |     
320 |     if joint in STANDING_POSE:
321 |         expected = STANDING_POSE[joint]
322 |         if abs(init_pos - expected) > 0.01:
323 |             print(f"⚠️  Joint '{joint}': joint initial_position {init_pos:.3f} "
324 |                   f"doesn't match standing pose {expected:.3f}")
325 | ```
