393 |     
394 |     if abs(pitch - 0.12) > 0.02:
395 |         print(f"⚠️  Model pitch {pitch:.3f} != 0.12 rad (may cause fall on spawn)")
396 |         print(f"   Expected: 0.12 rad (6.9°) forward lean to compensate for CoM")
397 | ```
