564 | ### 1. Remove Duplicate Friction Tags
565 | ```python
566 | # Keep last friction value, remove duplicates
567 | sdf_content = re.sub(
568 |     r'(<friction>[^<]+</friction>)\s*<friction>([^<]+)</friction>',
569 |     r'<friction>\2</friction>',
